title: South Africa : number of internet users 2017 to 2023
yAxis: Number of internet users in millions
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of internet users in millions. In total the number of data points it has is 7.
In general Number of internet users in millions has rose over the Year.
Number of internet users in millions is slightly increasing from 2017 to 2023.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
The highest Number of internet users in millions, of value 49.0 was reached at Year 2023
Minimum Number of internet users in millions about 33.9 was reached at Year 2017
